    <abstract id="aspace_d61518da22761c2cf5e1a1ec998d2625">A letter from Lanier Eason to Kitty and Hank Terjen discussing the author's memories of members of the Roebling family, dated 1976. The Roeblings designed and built the Brooklyn Bridge. Eason's mother (not named) appears from the letter to have known or married into the Roebling family.</abstract>
